   <talk_paragraph index="n2067_nophee-accepting" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_Nophee.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2067_nophee-accepting-acceptted" mid="186" select_type="3" />
      <talk_question mid="98"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>(Norfe smiles bitterly. I guess trying to comfort him would cause him more pain.)<BR>Is there anything I can do to help Grele get better?</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1816_vernicka-1" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Left_vernicka.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1816_vernicka-1-" mid="187" select_type="5" />
      <talk_question mid="99"><![CDATA[<html>$President Vernicka$<BR><FONT color=#7e12d2>(Vernicka looks too occupied now. He doesn't even seem to realise you're here.)</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2183_merca_arc-1" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="NPC_Right_arc.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2183_merca_arc-1-" mid="188" select_type="5" />
      <talk_question mid="100"><![CDATA[<html>$Arc$<BR>I have a feeling this will be a turning point for many things.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2067_nophee-1" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_Nophee.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2067_nophee-1-a" mid="189" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="101"><![CDATA[<html>$Norfe$<BR>Well, both Anna and I think that whatever treatment wouldn't work as well as retrieving Grele's jewel... Grele can recover by himself if he has his <FONT color=#a82424>jewel</FONT> back.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2067_nophee-1-a" image="QN_Child_Mammon.dds" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_Nophee.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2067_nophee-1-b" mid="190" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="102"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#086171>Grele's jewel</FONT><FONT color=#662500>…? We can get it back if we kill </FONT><FONT color=#a82424>Child Mamon</FONT><FONT color=#662500>, can't we?</FONT><BR><FONT color=#662500>Do you think it's possible?</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2067_nophee-1-b" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_Nophee.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2067_nophee-1-c" mid="191" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="103"><![CDATA[<html>$Norfe$<BR><FONT color=#7e12d2>(Norfe nods.)</FONT> As you've seen it for yourself, Mamon was in agony after she swallowed Grele's jewel. She must be having a hard time trying to absorb a jewel of a Child who is much stronger than her.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2067_nophee-1-c" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_Nophee.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2067_nophee-1-d" mid="192" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="104"><![CDATA[<html>$Norfe$<BR>I'm guessing Mamon will soon create a <FONT color=#a82424>Nest</FONT> to concentrate on fusing the jewels.<BR>
I think we can use that chance.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2067_nophee-1-d" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_Nophee.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2067_nophee-1-e" mid="193" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="105"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>That's a relief. It means we can get Grele's jewel back.</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2067_nophee-1-e" image="QN_grugiru.dds" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_Nophee.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2067_nophee-1-f" mid="194" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="106"><![CDATA[<html>$Norfe$<BR>But still, Mamon is a Child with numerous soldiers so we need to be fully prepared.<BR>Luckily, we have a helper. <FONT color=#086171>Gregory</FONT> said he knows the way to <FONT color=#a82424>Mamon's palace</FONT>.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2067_nophee-1-f" image="QN_grugiru.dds" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_Nophee.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2067_nophee-1-g" mid="195" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="107"><![CDATA[<html>$Norfe$<BR>I'm going to let <FONT color=#086171>Gregory</FONT> be the guide.<BR>If he does his job well, I'll seriously consider accepting him as a member of the Anti-Goddess Faction.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2067_nophee-1-g" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_Nophee.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2067_nophee-1-h" mid="196" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="108"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>Are you sure? But you were wary that Gregory is a Child.</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2067_nophee-1-h" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_Nophee.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2067_nophee-1-i" mid="197" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="109"><![CDATA[<html>$Norfe$<BR>This concerns Grele's life. Grele is a precious <FONT color=#a82424>mutant Child</FONT> to us…<BR>
We have to do whatever we can to save him. Besides, if Gregory joins us, we can let him take care of certain things that were beyond our means.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2067_nophee-1-i" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_Nophee.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2067_nophee-1-j" mid="198" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="110"><![CDATA[<html>$Norfe$<BR>Things have become more confusing now. It's fortunate that the evacuation preparations are almost done…<BR>After saving Grele, I will do my best to help you find the Chalice of Healing.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2067_nophee-1-j" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_Nophee.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2067_nophee-1-k" mid="199" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="111"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>All right. I'm sure Geraint will come back with some clues.</FONT><BR>
<FONT color=#662500>We can leave it until then.</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2067_nophee-1-k" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_Nophee.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2067_nophee-1-l" mid="200" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="112"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>By the way, Norfe… There's something I want to do first...</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2067_nophee-1-l" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_Nophee.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2067_nophee-1-m" mid="201" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="113"><![CDATA[<html>$Norfe$<BR>What is it?</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2067_nophee-1-m" image="QN_Vernicka.dds" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_Nophee.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2067_nophee-1-n" mid="202" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="114"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR>I want to go to <FONT color=#a82424>Merca's Heart</FONT><FONT color=#662500> and demand an explanation from </FONT><FONT color=#086171>Vernicka</FONT><FONT color=#662500>. I want to know why he did such things.</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2067_nophee-1-n" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_Nophee.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2067_nophee-1-o" mid="203" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="115"><![CDATA[<html>$Norfe$<BR>……I see. We should make him hold the responsibility for lighting up the fuse.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2067_nophee-1-o" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_Nophee.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2067_nophee-1-p" mid="204" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="116"><![CDATA[<html>$Norfe$<BR>He wouldn't admit that he has done something that can be considered as a betrayal to the Anti-Goddess Faction easily…<BR>
<FONT color=#387206>{user_nick}</FONT>, please wait for a while.<BR>
<FONT color=#7e12d2>(Norfe goes inside the tent and quickly scribbles something on a piece of paper.)</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2067_nophee-1-p" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_Nophee.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2067_nophee-1-q" mid="205" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="117"><![CDATA[<html>$Norfe$<BR>Please take this with you, it will help. It's a warning letter to Vernicka.<BR>
You can read it too if you want.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2067_nophee-1-q" image="QW_Merca_Cityhall.dds" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_Nophee.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2067_nophee-2" mid="206" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="118"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>Thanks. I'll make my way to </FONT><FONT color=#a82424>Merca's Heart</FONT><FONT color=#662500> now.</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2067_nophee-2" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_Nophee.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_question mid="119"><![CDATA[<html>$Norfe$<BR>Please be safe. I'll keep my eyes on Mamon.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1816_vernicka-2" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Left_vernicka.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1816_vernicka-2-a" mid="208" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="120"><![CDATA[<html>$President Vernicka$<BR>…<FONT color=#387206>{user_nick}</FONT>, I knew you'd come. I don't know why but Grele suddenly stormed to the Distorted Zone. Our guards tried to stop him but they were helpless...</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1816_vernicka-2-a" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Left_vernicka.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1816_vernicka-2-b" mid="209" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="121"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#7e12d2>(Stop Vernicka's speech.)</FONT><FONT color=#662500> </FONT><BR><FONT color=#662500>You know very well why Grele when to the Distorted Zone. Are you still trying to fool me?</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1816_vernicka-2-b" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Left_vernicka.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1816_vernicka-2-c" mid="210" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="122"><![CDATA[<html>$President Vernicka${sound:npc_Vernicka_9778_qu_01.ogg}<BR><FONT color=#7e12d2>(Vernicka cringes his face.)</FONT>Well... so you know everything now.<BR>But I've always been telling you that Hiver would be a threat to the Anti-Goddess Faction in the long term. She had to die at some point.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1816_vernicka-2-c" image="QN_Child_Mammon.dds" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Left_vernicka.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1816_vernicka-2-d" mid="211" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="123"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>You don't know what happened exactly, do you? Hiver ran away and Grele is hurt instead.<BR>He was attacked by Child Mamon, the Child you were collaborating with, and he even lost his jewel!</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1816_vernicka-2-d" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Left_vernicka.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1816_vernicka-2-e" mid="212" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="124"><![CDATA[<html>$President Vernicka$<BR>What did you just say…?!</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1816_vernicka-2-e" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Left_vernicka.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1816_vernicka-2-f" mid="213" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="125"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>Only Grele got hurt and he's on the verge of death right now!</FONT><BR><FONT color=#662500>If we don't do something, he'll disintegrate soon. It's all because of you!!</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1816_vernicka-2-f" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Left_vernicka.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1816_vernicka-2-g" mid="214" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="126"><![CDATA[<html>$President Vernicka$<BR>I guess I was too careless... I thought Grele would be strong enough to defeat Mamon.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1816_vernicka-2-g" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Left_vernicka.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1816_vernicka-2-h" mid="215" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="127"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>Why did you do it? Why!! Why did you sell Hiver's information to Mamon?</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1816_vernicka-2-h" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Left_vernicka.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1816_vernicka-2-i" mid="216" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="128"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>Did you have to go to such an extent to kill Hiver? Did you have to betray Grele and the Anti-Goddess Faction?</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1816_vernicka-2-i" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Left_vernicka.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1816_vernicka-2-j" mid="217" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="129"><![CDATA[<html>$President Vernicka$<BR>Well, what I sold to Mamon was only the opportunity and the devices. I didn't reveal the secret of Childs to her.<BR>All I did was to slip the information that she can catch a powerful Child if she used those devices.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1816_vernicka-2-j" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Left_vernicka.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1816_vernicka-2-k" mid="218" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="130"><![CDATA[<html>$President Vernicka$<BR>But I agree that I have a part to be blamed.<BR>I should have made sure Grele stayed in Merca. If I did, the plan would have been successful.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1816_vernicka-2-k" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Left_vernicka.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1816_vernicka-2-l" mid="219" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="131"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>Vernicka...... I trusted you. So did Norfe.</FONT><BR>
<FONT color=#662500>Do you know why?</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1816_vernicka-2-l" image="QN_Hiver.dds" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Left_vernicka.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1816_vernicka-2-m" mid="220" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="132"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>Because </FONT><FONT color=#086171>Hiver</FONT><FONT color=#662500> said we need to trust you.</FONT><BR>She told us <FONT color=#a94407>we cannot start or change anything if we don't give our trust first</FONT><FONT color=#662500>!</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1816_vernicka-2-m" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Left_vernicka.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1816_vernicka-3" mid="221" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="133"><![CDATA[<html>$President Vernicka$<BR>……That was a very naive thing to say.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1816_vernicka-3" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Left_vernicka.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1816_vernicka-3-a" mid="222" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="134"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>Seriously... No, not at all.</FONT><BR>
<FONT color=#662500>Since I'm not a Mistlander, you wouldn't believe whatever I say.</FONT><BR>
<FONT color=#662500>Here is Norfe's letter.</FONT><FONT color=#7e12d2> (Hold the letter right in front of Vernicka's face and start reading it aloud.)</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1816_vernicka-3-a" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="Npc_Left_Hologram.dds" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1816_vernicka-3-b" mid="223" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="135"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#086171>"Dear President Vernicka, although your plan was meticulously devised, you can see the tragic results for yourself. Due to your botch up, the Anti-Goddess Faction almost lost Grele, our most precious asset.</FONT><BR><FONT color=#086171>But we're not the only ones who would suffer from this incident."</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1816_vernicka-3-b" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="Npc_Left_Hologram.dds" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1816_vernicka-3-c" mid="224" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="136"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#086171>"President Vernicka, you have made the mistake of breaking the balance of power that was precariously in check. More importantly, you've lost our trust. Merca is a city that thrives on the conflict between the Goddess Followers and the Anti-Goddess Faction so I'm sure you know very well how losing our trust would affect your city in the long run.</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1816_vernicka-3-c" image="QN_Child_Mammon.dds" itemindex="" portrait_left="Npc_Left_Hologram.dds" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1816_vernicka-3-d" mid="225" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="137"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#086171>"Merca would also be in a dire situation in the near future. </FONT><FONT color=#a82424>Child Mamon</FONT><FONT color=#086171> is aborbing Grele's jewel right now so she is not taking any action, but where would she attack next when she recovers?</FONT><BR>
<FONT color=#086171>Merca's Heart is a strategic location with mines full of Goldstones. Your city will be her next target.</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1816_vernicka-3-d" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="Npc_Left_Hologram.dds" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1816_vernicka-3-e" mid="226" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="138"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#086171>"The Anti-Goddess Faction in the Southern Lands is closest to Mamon's territory and it's us who can find out about her activities more quickly than anyone else.</FONT><BR><FONT color=#086171>If you're not thinking of turning away from the Anti-Goddess Faction for good, I hope you can make the right decision this time."</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1816_vernicka-3-e" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Left_vernicka.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1816_vernicka-3-f" mid="227" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="139"><![CDATA[<html>$President Vernicka$<BR><FONT color=#7e12d2>(After listening to Norfe's letter, Vernicka turns pale.)</FONT><BR>
……He's right. Damn it.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1816_vernicka-3-f" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Left_vernicka.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1816_vernicka-3-g" mid="228" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="140"><![CDATA[<html>$President Vernicka${sound:npc_Vernicka_9778_qu_02.ogg}<BR>I admit, I didn't expect things would turn out this way. <FONT color=#7e12d2>(Vernicka snatches the letter from your hand and puts it inside his pocket.)</FONT><BR>Go and tell Norfe that I admit all my mistakes and would like to send my apologies.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1816_vernicka-3-g" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Left_vernicka.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1816_vernicka-3-h" mid="229" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="141"><![CDATA[<html>$President Vernicka$<BR>We will support money, men, ...whatever you need to treat Grele. I will send my soldiers too if the Anti-Goddess Faction needs them. I promise my full support for the Anti-Goddess Faction for it to regain stability.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1816_vernicka-3-h" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Left_vernicka.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1816_vernicka-3-i" mid="230" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="142"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>You only bow down when you hear that Merca is in trouble.</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1816_vernicka-3-i" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Left_vernicka.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1816_vernicka-3-j" mid="231" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="143"><![CDATA[<html>$President Vernicka${sound:npc_Vernicka_9778_qu_03.ogg}<BR>……Merca's Heart is all I care about.<BR><FONT color=#7e12d2>(Vernicka mumbles to himself.)</FONT> At least until <FONT color=#a82424>she</FONT> comes back……</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1816_vernicka-3-j" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Left_vernicka.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1816_vernicka-3-k" mid="232" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="144"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>Okay, I'll convey your message to Norfe. One last thing...<BR>Were you lying about </FONT><FONT color=#086171>Hiver's relics</FONT><FONT color=#662500> </FONT><FONT color=#662500>too?</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1816_vernicka-3-k" image="QN_Hiver.dds" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Left_vernicka.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1816_vernicka-3-l" mid="233" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="145"><![CDATA[<html>$President Vernicka$<BR>I was speaking the truth when I said we found Hiver's relics.<BR><FONT color=#a82424>Hiver's dagger</FONT> and a <FONT color=#a82424>set of new clothes</FONT> for her little brother were left behind by her.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1816_vernicka-3-l" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Left_vernicka.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1816_vernicka-3-m" mid="234" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="146"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>How could you do such things after looking at the remains of Hiver's past...?<BR>How can you bear to kill her?</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1816_vernicka-3-m" image="QN_Hiver.dds" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Left_vernicka.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1816_vernicka-3-n" mid="235" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="147"><![CDATA[<html>$President Vernicka${sound:npc_Vernicka_9778_qu_04.ogg}<BR><FONT color=#7e12d2>(Vernicka quietly mumbles after a short pause.)</FONT><BR>Human Hiver would have preferred to die.<BR>Rather than becoming a monster who kills her own family, she would rather...</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1816_vernicka-3-n" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Left_vernicka.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1816_vernicka-3-o" mid="236" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="148"><![CDATA[<html>$President Vernicka${sound:npc_Vernicka_9778_qu_05.ogg}<BR><FONT color=#7e12d2>(Vernicka stops talking and turns away.)</FONT><BR>Grele left Hiver's relics behind. I'll send them to the Southern Lands later.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1816_vernicka-3-o" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Left_vernicka.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1816_vernicka-3-p" mid="237" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="149"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>……Vernicka, even after going through all this, I want to continue to put my trust in you.</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1816_vernicka-3-p" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Left_vernicka.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1816_vernicka-3-q" mid="238" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="150"><![CDATA[<html>$President Vernicka$<BR>That's a relief. It would have been trouble for me if my precious relationship with a Lagendian ended here.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1816_vernicka-3-q" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Left_vernicka.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1816_vernicka-3-r" mid="239" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="151"><![CDATA[<html>$President Vernicka$<BR><FONT color=#7e12d2>(Vernicka closes his eyes like he doesn't want to talk anymore.</FONT><BR>
<FONT color=#7e12d2>It's the first time you see him so distressed.)</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1816_vernicka-3-r" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1816_vernicka-3-s" mid="240" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="152"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>(Is it just me or does he really have the guilty look on his face…?<BR>…What should I do now? Who should I trust and where should I go from here? I don't know.)</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1816_vernicka-3-s" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1816_vernicka-4" mid="259" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="258"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>(…What would </FONT><FONT color=#a94407>Geraint</FONT><FONT color=#662500> say if he's around? </FONT><FONT color=#2b2723>Argenta</FONT><FONT color=#662500> would have given me an earful of scolding…<BR>What would </FONT><FONT color=#a82424>Rubinart</FONT><FONT color=#662500> do if he was here? What would </FONT><FONT color=#086171>Meriendel</FONT><FONT color=#662500> do…)</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1816_vernicka-4" image="QW_Rubinat_Hideout.dds" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1816_vernicka-4-" mid="241" select_type="5" />
      <talk_question mid="153"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>(I don't know what to do or where to go from here…</FONT><BR><FONT color=#662500>…Maybe I should clear my head in </FONT><FONT color=#086171>Rubinart's Hideout</FONT><FONT color=#662500>.)</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2183_merca_arc-4" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="NPC_Right_arc.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2183_merca_arc-4-a" mid="242" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="154"><![CDATA[<html>$Arc$<BR><FONT color=#387206>{user_nick}</FONT>...</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2183_merca_arc-4-a" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="NPC_Right_arc.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2183_merca_arc-4-b" mid="243" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="155"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>Arc? What are you doing here……?</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2183_merca_arc-4-b" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="NPC_Right_arc.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2183_merca_arc-4-c" mid="244" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="156"><![CDATA[<html>$Arc$<BR>I heard what happened from Lord Norfe.<BR>He told me you were going to Merca's Heart and I thought maybe you'd make your way here…</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2183_merca_arc-4-c" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="NPC_Right_arc.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2183_merca_arc-4-d" mid="245" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="157"><![CDATA[<html>$Arc${sound:npc_Ark_9778_qu_01.ogg}<BR>Such a terrible thing happened. You must be feeling upset.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2183_merca_arc-4-d" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="NPC_Right_arc.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2183_merca_arc-4-e" mid="246" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="158"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>…I ...I couldn't stop Grele from getting hurt.</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2183_merca_arc-4-e" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="NPC_Right_arc.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2183_merca_arc-4-f" mid="247" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="159"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>I didn't realise Vernicka was plotting something behind our back,</FONT><BR>
<FONT color=#662500>and I wasted time trying to hide the fact that the devices looked like what Hiver made in the past...</FONT><BR>
<FONT color=#662500>…I couldn't find any clues on the </FONT><FONT color=#a82424>Chalice of Healing</FONT><FONT color=#662500> either…<BR><BR></FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2183_merca_arc-4-f" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="NPC_Right_arc.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2183_merca_arc-4-g" mid="248" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="160"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>It feels like there were so many things going on but I couldn't solve any of them.</FONT><BR><FONT color=#662500>I feel lost…….</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2183_merca_arc-4-g" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="NPC_Right_arc.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2183_merca_arc-4-h" mid="249" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="161"><![CDATA[<html>$Arc$<BR><FONT color=#2b2723>It's only natural for you to feel lost.<BR><FONT color=#387206>{user_nick}</FONT><FONT color=#2b2723>,</FONT><FONT color=#387206> </FONT><FONT color=#2b2723> it's not your fault. You did your best.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2183_merca_arc-4-h" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="NPC_Right_arc.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2183_merca_arc-4-i" mid="250" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="162"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>Thanks for saying that...</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2183_merca_arc-4-i" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="NPC_Right_arc.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2183_merca_arc-4-j" mid="251" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="163"><![CDATA[<html>$Arc$<BR>I'm sorry I'm not good in comforting others.<BR>…Since I found you here, I guess it's here where I will bid my farewell.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2183_merca_arc-4-j" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="NPC_Right_arc.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2183_merca_arc-4-k" mid="252" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="164"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>Are you leaving?</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2183_merca_arc-4-k" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="NPC_Right_arc.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2183_merca_arc-4-l" mid="253" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="165"><![CDATA[<html>$Arc${sound:npc_Ark_9778_qu_02.ogg}<BR>Yes. There's something I have to do and I can't stay in one place for long…<BR><FONT color=#2b2723>I will come back and find you if I find any clues on the </FONT><FONT color=#a82424>Chalice of Healing</FONT>.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2183_merca_arc-4-l" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="NPC_Right_arc.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2183_merca_arc-4-m" mid="254" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="166"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>Okay. </FONT><FONT color=#662500>I'll stay here and think for a while more.</FONT><BR>
<FONT color=#662500>I still don't know what I should do……</FONT><FONT color=#662500>.</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2183_merca_arc-4-m" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="NPC_Right_arc.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2183_merca_arc-4-n" mid="255" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="167"><![CDATA[<html>$Arc${sound:npc_Ark_9778_qu_03.ogg}<BR>Maybe it's time for you to take a break.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2183_merca_arc-4-n" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="NPC_Right_arc.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2183_merca_arc-4-o" mid="256" select_type="4" />
      <talk_question mid="168"><![CDATA[<html>$Quest Reward$</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2183_merca_arc-4-o" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="NPC_Right_arc.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2183_merca_arc-4-p" mid="264" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="169"><![CDATA[<html>$Arc$<BR>Gregory should be at Red Waste. If you need a guidance, I can join you before you leave.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2183_merca_arc-4-p" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2183_merca_arc-4-q" mid="267" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="266"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>No, that’s fine. I’ve met him several times before at Red Waste, so I think I know where to find him.</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2183_merca_arc-4-q" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="NPC_Right_arc.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_question mid="268"><![CDATA[<html>$Arc$<BR>I understand. It makes me think that many things will change with this incident.<BR>Nevertheless, please do not reproach yourself, traveller from Althea.<BR>Do not let yourself sink into dejection and lose your good will.</html>]]></talk_question>
